Name: King War [RTS]
About the game: The continuation of the End War RTS, the use of pure new real-time placement units, the attack of important strategic points, the game playing method of competing for economic advantages, and the new playing method not available in the previous series of games such as End War RTS King War [RTS] map system can automatically generate a new map by setting the size and water area size The King War [RTS] world is composed of eight camps of the United States, France, Britain, Germany, Russia, Cuba, Libya and aliens. The power and weapon units of each country are different. The American aerospace aircraft carrier, the Russian missile submarine and other features King War [RTS] There are a large number of weapon units in the world. With the rich land, sea and air play, expanding your army needs to obtain more minerals. Crazy occupation of more resources is your primary strategic goal. Build more mines, more mining cars, use metal storms, lightning towers and other defense structures to hold your position, ground power lightning tanks, long-range strike missiles, air power aircraft carriers God's particle ND500 warships are your powerful force King War [RTS] inherits the characteristics of End War RTS. The advanced alien race can be developed in a rolling way. It is the strongest race in the King War [RTS] world, and the time resurrection technology is the killer of the alien race
